" relacionadas con los objetivos pueden consultarse en la tabla SO1.IA.T1."

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../voluntary_targets_and_others.md:98
msgid ""
"If Parties already reported implemented actions in PRAIS as part of their "
"2022 national report, they will be pre-filled in this table."
msgstr ""
"Si las Partes ya informaron de las acciones implementadas en PRAIS como "
